; Menus

autmenu=Automatic Baking Items|0|false|The original automatic baking menu, a staple of the game since version 1.0. These are the core upgrades that keep your ovens running around the clock.
mabimenu=Manual Baking Items|0|false|The original manual baking menu, also a staple since version 1.0. These upgrades reward the hands-on baker who likes to get their fingers doughy.
usermenu=User Created Items|5|false|Custom items that were created by the community.

; Items

